  <brief_title>Sino-nasal Inhalation of Colistin in Patients With Cystic Fibrosis and Pseudomonas Aeruginosa Colonization</brief_title>
  <official_title>Sino-nasal Inhalation of Colistin Via the Pari Sinus Nebulizer in Patients With Cystic Fibrosis and Colonization of the Upper Airways With Pseudomonas Aeruginosa</official_title>
